new file -> app.js
app.js -> npm init -y
install nodemon 
install modul express -> npm i express
install modul ejs(templating engine) -> npm i ejs
install express ejs layout -> npm i express-ejs-layouts
install module mongodb -> npm i mongoose
install express session -> npm i express-session
install cookie parser -> npm i cookie-parser
install flash message -> npm i connect-flash
install express-validator -> npm i express-validator
install method-override -> npm i method-override

require modules express
require modules flash
require mongodb connection 
require model(collection db)

call app express and set port

configuration server

-setup EJS view engine
-setup express layouts
-setup express static for public folder (img,css,files.., etc)

build get / for index.ejs as Home page

Make Utils folder
Make db.js file for mongodb connection
Make Model folder
make contact.js for Schema db
Set Schema

Make Folder Views
Make Folder layouts in Views
-build layouts/main-layout.ejs
-build nav.ejs
Folder Views
-index.ejs
-about.ejs
-contact.ejs

Make Route
get / for index as Home page
get /about for about.ejs as about
get /contact for contact.ejs as contact
get /contact/add for add-contact.ejs as adding new contact
post /contact for add-contact.ejs as proses adding new contact
get /contact/:nama for detail.ejs as detail contact




